ed on UNIX](https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.2/manual/cmake.1.html#unix-specific-command-line-tools), ~~the ExternalProject_Add call is also restricted to UNIX systems~~ the files are copied one-by-one for non-unix systems (25f8aee)", "title": "add an example with ExternalProject", "destination": {"commit": {"hash": "981c6eda3e1f", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commit/981c6eda3e1f.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commits/981c6eda3e1f"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}ts=default"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-cmake", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake", "uuid": "{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}"}, "branch": {"name": "default"}}, "reason": "", "source": {"commit": {"hash": "adf3f61d58eb", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commit/adf3f61d58eb.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commits/adf3f61d58eb"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}ts=default"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-cmake", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake", "uuid": "{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}"}, "branch": {"name": "example"}}, "state": "OPEN", "author": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "date": "2017-10-24T00:39:56.945520+00:00"}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 7, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/7.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/7"}}, "title": "add an example with ExternalProject"}}, {"comment": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/7/comments/47819715.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/7/_/diff#comment-47819715"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 7, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/7.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/7"}}, "title": "add an example with ExternalProject"}, "content": {"raw": "Maybe add something to this comment to indicate that the `N` in `cmakeN` is not a typo. For example:\n\n    # find_package expects cmakeN (e.g. cmake0, cmake1, ... depending on the major version of ign-cmake) to be in the build folder because that is where the uninstalled ignition-cmake-config.cmake file is located.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Maybe add something to this comment to indicate that the <code>N</code> in <code>cmakeN</code> is not a typo. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span># find_package expects cmakeN (e.g. cmake0, cmake1, ... depending on the major version of ign-cmake) to be in the build folder because that is where the uninstalled ignition-cmake-config.cmake file is located.\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-10-24T00:30:10.675517+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/us