y were changed", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>after discussions with @mxgrey, I added support for non-Unix systems by copying the <code>cmake</code> folder files to the build folder one-by-one</p>\n<p>note that I used <code>configure_file</code> with <code>COPYONLY</code> (as recommended <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/34800667\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>) so the files would be re-copied if they were changed</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-10-24T00:26:14.610842+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": "2017-10-24T00:26:14.619964+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 47819576}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 7, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/7.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/7"}}, "title": "add an example with ExternalProject"}}, {"update": {"description": "I've added a minimal example of a package that uses ignition-cmake and calls `ign_configure_build` but goes no further. This requires CMakeLists.txt files to exist in the `doc`, `include`, `src`, and `test` folders.\r\n\r\nI also used `ExternalProject_Add` so that the examples will be built during `make`. I had to do two funky things in 08ccbf3 to allow the external project to `find_package(ignition-cmake0)` without actually installing `ignition-cmake`:\r\n\r\n* set the `CMAKE_PREFIX_PATH` in a cmake arg to the external project\r\n* create symlink in build folder to the `cmake` folder in the source. Since the `create_symlink` cmake command is [only supported on UNIX](https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.2/manual/cmake.1.html#unix-specific-command-line-tools), the `ExternalProject_Add` call is also restricted to UNIX systems", "title": "add an example with ExternalProject", "destination": {"commit": {"hash": "981c6eda3e1f", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commit/981c6eda3e1f.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commits/981c6eda3e1f"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}ts=default"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-cmake", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake", "uuid": "{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}"}, "branch": {"name": "default"}}, "reason": "", "source": {"commit": {"hash": "d2ba251303c3", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commit/d2ba251303c3.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commits/d2ba251303c3"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}ts=default"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-cmake", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake", "uuid": "{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}"}, "branch": {"name": "example"}}, "state": "OPEN", "author": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%